data.description: This Beautiful 4-bedroom, 2 FULL bathroom POOL home with Florida Room offers 1944 sqft of living space. Situated on nearly a 1 acre lot, it boasts a spacious kitchen and a HUGE backyard already fenced in. Every corner of this home has been touched, including new impact windows, newer ROOF, newer AC, newer hot water heater and new sprinkler irrigation pump. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle you deserve. Transform the yard to your own oasis with ample outdoor space! You will own a home in a terrific neighborhood, close to schools, shopping, and restaurants. Take a bike ride to Sugar Mill Gardens or Our famous beach is only a 6 min drive away. The Intercostal river and bridge is just a 3 min drive. This turnkey home is ready and waiting for new owners. Don't miss out call today for your showing!
